::DarkMouse::

She took small and uneasy steps while holding onto Quickstrike.  She 
was at least walking a little and that helped to lift her spirits.
"I"ll make it. Just walk slow for bit.  I got to get used to this 
again. Do yurself a favor, if you die, don't come back. It's not all 
it's cracked up to be." she said with a slight chuckle. She started 
shaking again.  She had to take even smaller steps to keep from 
falling down.
